threads.title: 820-3330 no image
threads.message:
It chimes with backlight. no image. i also have tried external display and nothing, even with LCD cable unplug.


PPvcore_gpu = 0.9v
L8360 = 0v (should be 1.36v) - resistance to GND on L8360 is 172 ohms
PP3V3_S0GPU = 3.3v
GPUVcore_en = 3.3v
P3V3GPU_EN = 3.3v
PPVIN_S5_HS_GPU_ISNS = 12.58v

I've already replaced U8900, I've reflowed the old and its still same,

yes. there seems to be USB activity. I've tried other bios from a donor board for testing and its the same.

threads.title: 820-3330 no image
threads.message:
You are missing vRAM voltage; can't get GPU working.
Check U8350 voltages; pins 15, 19, 20.
Be sure R8359 and C8355 are OK.
Also check all traces and resistors aroun U8350.

You may need to change U8350 and/or Q8360...
